quran[11{c,v,t}:
7,196,Inna waliyyial laahul lazee nazzalal Kitaaba wa Huwa yatawallas saaliheen
7,197,Wallazeena tad'oona min doonihee laa yastatee'oona nasrakum wa laaa anfusahum yansuroon
7,198,Wa in tad'oohum ilal hudaa laa yasm'oo wa taraahum yanzuroona ilaika wa hum laa yubsiroon
7,199,khuzil 'afwa waamur bil'urfi waa'rid 'anil jaahileen
7,200,Wa immaa yanzaghannaka minash Shaitaani nazghun fasta'iz billaah; innahoo Samee'un Aleem
7,201,Innal lazeenat taqaw izaa massahum taaa'ifum minash Shaitaani tazakkaroo fa izaa hum mubsiroon
7,202,Wa ikhwaanuhum yamuddoonahum fil ghaiyi summa laa yuqsiroon
7,203,Wa izaa lam taatihim bi aayatin qaaloo law lajtabai tahaa; qul innamaaa attabi'u maa yoohaaa ilaiya mir Rabbee; haazaa basaaa'iru mir Rabbikum wa hudanw wa rahmatul liqawminy yu'minoon
7,204,Wa izaa quri'al Quraanu fastami'oo lahoo wa ansitoo la 'allakum turhamoon
7,205,Wazkur Rabbaka fee nafsika tadarru'anw wa kheefatanw wa doonal jahri minal qawli bilghuduwwi wal aasali wa laa takum minal ghaafileen
7,206,Innal lazeena 'inda Rabbika laa yastakbiroona 'an 'ibaadatihee wa yusabbihoonahoo wa lahoo yasjudoon (section 24)�(make sajda)
